description.en: CuraDAI is a digital currency that leverages the latest open financial tools built on blockchain technology to create a digital, stable and transparent currency that matches the local currency of Curaçao in terms of the unit of account. CuraDAI is 100% backed by Dai, a digital currency soft-pegged to the US Dollar.
